<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contact Us - Futuristic</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: black;
            color: #00ffff;
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            padding: 50px;
            border: 2px solid cyan;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px cyan;
            border-radius: 15px;
            background: rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.1);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
        }

        h1 {
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px cyan, 0 0 20px cyan;
            font-size: 3rem;
        }

        p {
            text-shadow: 0 0 5px cyan;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        label {
            text-shadow: 0 0 5px cyan;
        }

        .form-control {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            border: 1px solid cyan;
            color: #00ffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px cyan;
        }

        .form-control:focus {
            background-color: rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-color: cyan;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px cyan;
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-custom {
            background: transparent;
            border: 2px solid cyan;
            color: #00ffff;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 5px cyan, 0 0 10px cyan;
            transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }

        .btn-custom:hover {
            background: #00ffff;
            color: black;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px cyan, 0 0 20px cyan;
        }

        .alert-success {
            background-color: rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border: 1px solid cyan;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px cyan;
            color: white;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="headerContainer">
        <h1 id="mainHeader">About Us</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="info">
        <h3>Our Mission</h3>
        <p class="par">Neo Twitter is the new, futuristic look of Twitter, because X is too dull for new generations.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="info">
        <h3>Contact</h3>
        <p class="par">Reach out to us via <a href="deyzaguirre1@miuandes.cl">Email</a></p>
    </div>
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" id="button">Join The New Era</button>
</body>
</html>